description.narrative: To ascertain the viability of Index Based Livestock Insurance in Mongolia to reduce the impact of livestock mortality for herders' livelihoods through: (i) scaling up Index Based Livestock Insurance Program in Selected Aimags; and (ii) building the institutional capacity and legal and institutional framework for the sustainability of the Index Based Livestock Insurance Program.
